HEADWORD: Caricaceae
<hw>Caricaceae</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a natural family of trees native
to tropical America and Africa with milky juice and large palmately
lobed leaves.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> family <fam>Caricaceae</fam>, papaya
family.</syn>⟦br⟧
